ance Method","a":"Returns where the range of the selection that should be placed inside marked text."},{"t":"server()","p":"documentation/InputMethodKit/IMKInputController/server()","r":"Instance Method","a":"Returns the server object that manages the input controller."},{"t":"setAttributes(_:)","p":"documentation/InputMethodKit/IMKCandidates/setAttributes(_:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Sets the style attributes for the candidates window."},{"t":"setCandidateData(_:)","p":"documentation/InputMethodKit/IMKCandidates/setCandidateData(_:)","r":"Instance Method"},{"t":"setCandidateFrameTopLeft(_:)","p":"documentation/InputMethodKit/IMKCandidates/setCandidateFrameTopLeft(_:)","r":"Instance Method"},{"t":"setDelegate(_:)","p":"documentation/InputMethodKit/IMKInputController/setDelegate(_:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Sets the delegate for input controller  object."},{"t":"setDismissesAutomatically(_:)","p":"documentation/InputMethodKit/IMKCandidates/setDismissesAutomatically(_:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Sets the state of the flag that determines whether the candidates window dismisses automatically."},{"t":"setPanelType(_:)","p":"documentation/InputMethodKit/IMKCandidates/setPanelType(_:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Sets the style of the candidates window."},{"t":"setSelectionKeys(_:)","p":"documentation/InputMethodKit/IMKCandidates/setSelectionKeys(_:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Sets the selection keys for the candidates."},{"t":"setSelectionKeysKeylayout(_:)","p":"documentation/InputMethodKit/IMKCandidates/setSelectionKeysKeylayout(_:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Sets the key layout that is used to map virtual key codes to characters."},{"t":"setValue(_:forTag:client:)","p":"documentation/InputMethodKit/IMKStateSetting/setValue(_:forTag:client:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Set the value for the provided key."},{"t":"show()","p":"documentation/InputMethodKit/IMKCandidates/show()","r":"Instance Method"},{"t":"show(_:)","p":"documentation/InputMethodKit/IMKCandidates/